dc_title_s: C-21 Geologic atlas of Carver County, Minnesota [Part A]
dc_description_s: 5 pls. Scales 1:100,000 and 1:200,000. Pl. 1, data-base map; pl. 2, bedrock geology; pl. 3, surficial geology; pl. 4 Quaternary stratigraphy and sand distribution model; pl. 5, bedrock topography, depth to bedrock, and mineral endowment. Supplementary files include ArcGis coverages, shapefiles and/or ESRI grids used to construct the plates, and metadata.
